<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mn ly swạk ạ̉rjw kẖlạṣh ạlʿẓym
 wmn swạk ygẖny bfyḍh ạlʿmym
 lys ạtkạl qlby ʿly̱ ạlwry̱ ạlʿdym
 ffy ydyk ạ̉mry yạ ḥy yạ ʿlym
