 wydmʿn ldmʿy krqẗ ạlnsym
 mn hkdẖạ yʿzy wnwrh ydym
 wnfsy ạlḥzynẗ mn ạlrdy̱ yqym
 3- mn hkdẖạ yrạny kkẖlh ạlḥmym
 kṣnʿh ạlbdyʿ ạ̉rạh by yhym
 yḥwṭny bḥb nbʿ mn ạlṣmym
 wyʿtny bnfsy fy drbh ạlqwmy
 4- mn gẖyrk sybqy̱ ʿwny ʿly̱ ạlạ̉tẖym
 bbạ̉sk tnjy wqlbk ạlrḥym
 msyjaⁿạ ʿly fy ạlkẖṭr ạljsym
 bmrkbạt nạr wjndk ạlʿẓym</lyrics>
<title>mn ly swạk</title>
